comments: Grimes (NYK) places his forearm against Kuzma's (WAS) lower body as he enters his upward shooting motion, but he immediately removes it.
Wright (WAS) reaches in and marginal contact occurs with Brunson (NYK), who loses control of his dribble on his own.
Kuzma (WAS) moves alongside Randle's (NYK) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.

Replay review of the foul called on Robinson (NYK) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Robinson steps into Kuzma's (WAS) path and initiates body contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Hachimura (WAS) legally contests Grimes's (NYK) jump shot attempt.
Grimes (NYK) is in a legal guarding position alongside of Kuzma (WAS), whose leg is extended and creates the marginal contact.
Wright (WAS) commits a take foul on Randle (NYK).
Grimes (NYK) briefly places an arm around Porzingis (WAS) and the contact is marginal. Porzingis raises his own arms to draw attention to the contact.
Randle (NYK) applies a hand to Kuzma's (WAS) body with force that affects his jump shot attempt.
Brunson (NYK) inbounds the ball within five seconds.
Goodwin (WAS) commits a take foul on Brunson (NYK).
Barrett (NYK) legally contests Hachimura's (WAS) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Porzingis (WAS) commits a take foul on Brunson (NYK).
